title: How to Lead Your Team, with Andy Frisella - MFCEO8
description: In this special extended episode, Andy Frisella is joined by Washington Redskins linebacker Will Compton, as well as his co-hosts Vaughn Kohler and Ben Newman.  From leading by example to showing appreciation for your team, this is an insightful and comprehensive discussion.
